Description:
You arrive at a camp near the river, here you see a strange humanoid figure with a squid-like head and large black eyes that reflect the stars on the horizon, although it is not yet dark.

You have never seen anyone like him before, perhaps he is not from this world... as you approach he says to you:

"Hello travellers, don't be afraid, I see you have a promising future ahead of you.
DescriptionAction: If you wish, I can do a divination for you."
